1
00:00:00,400 --> 00:00:05,700
Schema risk hides behind a pull request.  ·  风险常常隐藏在看似普通的 Schema 变更里

2
00:00:05,700 --> 00:00:11,200
ChangeGuard decides before production.  ·  ChangeGuard 在上线前给出可审计决策

3
00:00:11,900 --> 00:00:19,500
Real DataHub graph: owner, tags, and lineage.  ·  真实 DataHub 图谱：负责人、标签与血缘

4
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:27,300
Field lineage reveals exact consumers.  ·  字段级血缘定位真正受影响的下游

5
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:35,600
Rename, type, and nullability changes.  ·  重命名、类型和空值约束三类风险

6
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:43,200
Renames require explicit evidence.  ·  重命名必须提供明确映射，系统不会猜测

7
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:51,500
Live evidence returns BLOCK at 100 out of 100.  ·  实时证据计算结果：BLOCK，风险 100/100

8
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:59,300
Every finding names affected assets.  ·  每项风险都指向具体受影响资产

9
00:00:59,900 --> 00:01:06,600
Compatibility SQL and a dbt contract.  ·  生成兼容 SQL 与 dbt 契约

10
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:13,200
Proposals only. Nothing is deployed.  ·  仅供审核，不会自动部署

11
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:21,700
Writeback requires two confirmation flags.  ·  写回必须经过两个显式确认参数

12
00:01:21,700 --> 00:01:29,000
The same audit cannot duplicate incidents.  ·  同一审计不会重复创建事件

13
00:01:29,700 --> 00:01:38,000
AI explains. Deterministic code enforces.  ·  AI 负责解释，确定性代码负责执行规则

14
00:01:38,000 --> 00:01:46,300
DataHub keeps the auditable record.  ·  DataHub 保存可审计的操作记录
